Day 39: Create a Docker Image From Container

Date: October 4, 2025
Overview
Created custom Docker images from modified containers.
Key Concepts Learned

Docker commit command
Image creation workflow
Container modifications
Image tagging

Commands Used
bashdocker commit container_name new_image_name:tag
docker tag image_id username/repository:tag
docker history image_name
Challenges Faced
Understanding that commit creates large images. Later learned Dockerfile is the better approach!
